OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779811864
OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FThunderstorms may be sparked in the
OL,7,Fafternoon, which will affect how hot
OL,8,Fit gets.
OL,10,F"So it's a trickier one to predict the
OL,11,Ftemperatures for tomorrow, definitely
OL,12,Fpotential for it to be hotter," Ms
OL,13,FMitchell said.
OL,15,FRecords may also be broken in the lead-
OL,16,Fup with forecasters warning some
OL,17,Fplaces may not drop below 20C
OL,18,Fovernight.
