OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FThis comes after the UK's warmest May
OL,7,Fnight was measured on Sunday when
OL,8,Ftemperatures did not fall below 19.4C
OL,9,Fat Kenley Airfield, Surrey.
OL,11,FMany places across England and Wales
OL,12,Fwill reach the heatwave threshold on
OL,13,FTuesday and some will have had five
OL,14,Fdays of it by Wednesday, Ms Mitchell
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
