PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779811864
OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FHeatwave conditions were already met
OL,7,Fin eight parts of England by Sunday
OL,8,Fnight: Heathrow, Kew Gardens and
OL,9,FNortholt London; Benson in
OL,10,FOxfordshire; Brooms Barn and Santon
OL,11,FDownham in Suffolk; High Beech and
OL,12,FWrittle in Essex.
OL,14,FThat number will be higher after the
OL,15,Fbank holiday weather but the data is
OL,16,Fyet to be released, Ms Mitchell said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
