OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FThe fact nearly a hundred sites
OL,7,Freached 30C on Monday "goes to show
OL,8,Fjust how many places would have
OL,9,Fsucceeded their heatwave threshold",
OL,10,Fshe added.
OL,12,FTo qualify as a heatwave, temperatures
OL,13,Fmust meet or surpass a specific
OL,14,Fthreshold for three consecutive days.
OL,16,FThe highest heatwave threshold in the
OL,17,FUK at this time of year is 28C, which
OL,18,Fapplies to London and north of the
OL,19,Fcapital towards Cambridgeshire.
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
