OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779811864
OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FTemperatures will start to gradually
OL,7,Fdecline from the middle of the week
OL,8,Fbut it will still be largely dry with
OL,9,Fsunny spells.
OL,11,FMany will still experience
OL,12,Ftemperatures in the high 20Cs.
OL,14,FHowever, they will lower by around 10C
OL,15,Fin eastern areas as a brisk easterly
OL,16,Fwind develops.
OL,18,FIf validated, the latest May record
OL,19,Fmeans seven of the 12 monthly highs
OL,20,Fhave been set since 2003, the Met
OL,21,FOffice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
