OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779811864
OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FA previous study by the forecasters
OL,7,Ffound breaking that record "is around
OL,8,Fthree times more likely now in our
OL,9,Fcurrent climate than it would have
OL,10,Fbeen in a natural climate not impacted
OL,11,Fby greenhouse gas emissions".
OL,13,FThis means that the once one-in-a-
OL,14,Fhundred year event is now a one-in-33
OL,15,Fevent, it said.
OL,17,FIt comes after last week saw lows of
OL,18,Fminus 5C in Scotland and daytime
OL,19,Ftemperatures more widely peaked at
OL,20,Fabout 14C to 15C.
OL,26,@oD@\OUsD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
