OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,F"We see these changes happening so
OL,7,Fmuch more dramatically," Met Office
OL,8,Fsenior forecaster Greg Dewhurst said
OL,9,Fon Monday morning, adding that climate
OL,10,Fchange is boosting the heat.
OL,12,F"In the past, heatwaves built and
OL,13,Fbuilt and built and built over days
OL,14,Fand days and days ` these now just
OL,15,Fdevelop so quickly."
OL,17,FAmid the bank holiday weekend heat,
OL,18,FSouth East Water apologised and handed
OL,19,Fout bottled water after about 502 of
OL,20,Fits customers had issues including
OL,21,Foutages and low pressure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XO]tD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
