OL,3,CMore temperature records could tumble
OL,4,Cafter scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FMeanwhile, fire and smoke spread
OL,7,Facross a large patch of Holyrood Park,
OL,8,FEdinburgh, above St Anthony's Chapel
OL,9,Fon Monday.
OL,11,FOn Sunday, Lincolnshire Police said
OL,12,Fthe body of 15-year-old Declan Sawyer
OL,13,Fwas recovered from the water at
OL,14,FSwanholme Lakes, Lincoln, after he had
OL,15,Fbeen reported to be in trouble that
OL,16,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
